==================================
=  README for ex2: Flow Control  =
==================================


usage:  1. python ex2_square.py
	2. python ex2_rpsls.py


==================
=  Description:  =
==================

In Task 1 I asked the user for number 'n' and printed a square of '#'
	in size of (2n+1)*(2n+1) with a rhombus inside with edge
	of n stars inside.
In task 2 I asked the user to choose number of rounds and then play 
	Rock-Paper-Scissors-Lizard-Spock until someone win. 

